by excusing all prospective jurors who initially wrote on the 
questionnaire that they hadnt been exposed to the north testimony 
but indicated during open court questioning that they had been 
prior to the filing by norths lawyers the judge added five 
people to the pool of prospective jurors including a man who said 
he tried to put a pillow over his head to avoid hearing anything 
