weekend gallup poll asked 1001 adults from friday through sunday 
whether they favored or opposed increasing congressional pay from 
89500 to 135000 the amount of the proposed increase 
the results with a fourpoint margin of error showed 82 percent 
opposed with only 15 percent in favor 
