the contras are expected to field candidates said descoto he said 
he did not know if president daniel ortega would run for reelection 
descoto also called on the united states to join the five 
central american nations in an antidrug treaty 
it would be noble and good and christian said descoto who 
is also a roman catholic priest 
he had no details but he said nicaragua would not object to the 
us drug enforcement agency having an office in nicaragua 
