with takeshitas liberal democratic party to give a semblance of 
unity when parliament passed the governments tax bill 
tsukamotos links to the recruit scandal then were seen as 
helping the governing liberal democrats push the tax bill through 
because the social democrats were as hobbled by the taint of scandal 
as the governing party and could not take any high moral position 
