board he would prefer leaving it as an independent regulatory agency 
but split off its oversight of the sampl deposit insurance fund 
committee chairman donald riegle dmich said he and sen jake 
garn of utah the panels ranking republican plan to introduce the 
administrations package as soon as it was submitted and schedule 
