inflationary impact on the economy as raising spending in such areas 
as defense 
on the question of raising the deposit insurance premiums 
volcker did not provide a specific amount that he would like to see 
but he said the bush recommendation came very close to the limits 
that the banks could bear 
the banks are having enough trouble competing now and i dont 
like to see any additional burdens put on them volcker said 
this goes toward the limits of what is tolerable 
